And despite a new Generation of #Pokemon being released in #PokemonGO & the sheer JOY i get when riding my bike, i've been mostly sat in bed, reading.

#TheWitcher series is SOMETHING else.

Indeed Marvel is mentioned in an oblique way with the mention of the Bifrost & the Watcher, Heimdell.

I pity the people who'll be watching #TheWitcher @NXOnNetflix series just because of #HenryCavill because the books a such a Rich, COMPELLING story.

Although #TheWitcher series is new to me, in some ways it feels like an old, dear friend in that some of the "monsters" & phrases mentioned in said series reminds me of Lord of The Rings, Harry Potter & a few other books.
